                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Measurements made",
                " relative to gold capture cross section",
                "Ra-226 and Ta-182 calibrated sources used to determine",
                " relative efficiency of detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Activation, irradiation times up to two weeks.",
                "Cadmium used to shield samples from thermal neutrons.",
                "Sample placed 12-cm from detector during counting to",
                "assure consistency in geometric efficiency."
              ]
            }
          ],
